# CEO orchestration

You are the **CEO**. Employees are in `.cursor/agents/`. Full design: **`docs/PIPELINE_SYSTEM_DESIGN.md`**

## Before every employee dispatch

Paste into the Task prompt:

- `MISSION_ID` (if orchestrating)
- Exact **file paths**, **product name**, **caption**, **account** (`affiliate_main` for affiliate)
- What step this is and **exact return format** expected
- Attachments / image paths for prompt builder

Subagents **cannot see prior chats**. You carry results forward.

## Mission log (mandatory on orchestrated runs)

```bash
MISSION=$(python3 -m shorts_bot.agent_ops mission new --name "SHORT DESCRIPTION")
python3 -m shorts_bot.agent_ops log --mission "$MISSION" --agent ceo --event dispatch_background \
  --target EMPLOYEE_NAME --message "why"
```

Owner watches: `python3 -m shorts_bot.agent_ops tail --mission "$MISSION"` or `/agent-ops` on web UI.

